overview.projectSummary: ELOP program for students, with a special emphasis on supporting underserved youth, integrating music with S.T.E.A.M. education.

functional: Nurturing creativity, critical thinking, and collaboration
Encouraging exploration of S.T.E.A.M. career opportunities
Fostering open communication and emotional expression through music
Offering diverse services encompassing creative S.T.E.A.M. exploration, teamwork and collaboration, and music for optimal wellness
technical: Personalized instruction in bass, lead guitar, keyboards, and drums
